1	// Smoke test for the deployed apify-webhook edge function (US-016, US-017,
2	// US-018).
3	//
4	// Usage: bun run scripts/test/apify-webhook.ts
5	// Requires SUPABASE_URL, SUPABASE_ANON_KEY, APIFY_WEBHOOK_SECRET in .env.
6	//
7	// Covers the paths that don't need a live Apify run — the SUCCEEDED branch
8	// (which pulls a real dataset) is exercised end-to-end in the iteration's
9	// MCP verification, not here.
10	//
11	// Asserts:
12	//   1.  Missing X-Apify-Webhook-Secret → 401 UNAUTHORIZED
13	//   2.  Wrong secret → 401 UNAUTHORIZED (constant-time reject)
14	//   3.  Malformed JSON body with valid secret → 400 INVALID_JSON
15	//   4.  Missing required fields → 400 INVALID_REQUEST
16	//   5.  Unknown scrape_mode → 200 { skipped:'unsupported_scrape_mode' }
17	//       (defensive coverage for the catch-all branch; tiktok_profile,
18	//        ig_details, and ig_posts are all live)
